name: Basic Graphic Design Course
discription: At present, most of the jobs in Freelancing are available in Graphics Design. You also need to learn graphic design to make a living by freelancing or to edit your own photos at work or as a hobby. So the Graphics Design course of Dragon Learning is giving Basic Photoshop & Illustrator lessons, through which you too can become a successful Freelancer.
